{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id0d5e7c8c-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s1095"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1095"},"text":"§ 1095.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Transfer of allotments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"In order to offer an arrangement of types of aid, including institutional and State aid which best fits the needs of each individual student, an institution may (1) transfer a total of 25 percent of the institutions ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"idref":"fn002109"},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"type":"footnote","id":"fn002109"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":" So in original. Probably should be “institution’s”."}],"tail":" allotment under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t20/s1087bb"},"text":"section 1087bb of this title","children":[],"tail":" to the institution’s allotment under section 1070b–3 or 1087–52 of this title (or both); (2) transfer 25 percent of the institution’s allotment under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t20/s1087–52"},"text":"section 1087–52 of this title","children":[],"tail":" to the institution’s allotment under section 1070b–3 or 1087bb of this title (or both); and (3) transfer 25 percent of the institution’s allotment under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t20/s1070b–3"},"text":"section 1070b–3 of this title","children":[],"tail":" to the institution’s allotment under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t20/s1087–52"},"text":"section 1087–52 of this title","children":[],"tail":". Funds transferred to an institution’s allotment under another section may be used as a part of and for the same purposes as funds allotted under that section. The Secretary shall have no control over such transfer, except as specifically authorized, except for the collection and dissemination of information."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id0d5e7c8d-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/89/329/tIV/s488"},"text":"Pub. L. 89–329, title IV, § 488","children":[],"tail":", as added "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/99/498/tIV/s407/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 99–498, title IV, § 407(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1986-10-17"},"text":"Oct. 17, 1986","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/100/1490"},"text":"100 Stat. 1490","children":[],"tail":"; amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/100/50/s15/14"},"text":"Pub. L. 100–50, § 15(14)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1987-06-03"},"text":"June 3, 1987","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/101/357"},"text":"101 Stat. 357","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/325/tIV/s492"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–325, title IV, § 492","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1992-07-23"},"text":"July 23, 1992","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/106/630"},"text":"106 Stat. 630","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/110/315/tIV/s494A"},"text":"Pub. L. 110–315, title IV, § 494A","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2008-08-14"},"text":"Aug. 14, 2008","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/122/3319"},"text":"122 Stat. 3319","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id0d5e7c8e-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id0d5e7c8f-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"ta